data.description: Charming and clean home situated on the back of a quiet court.  Be sure to not miss this home in Jacaranda West.  Light and bright with large windows for great natural light.  Upon entering you will look through your new living room with 4 large pocket sliders to your glass and screen enclosed Florida room overlooking your private screened pool.  Split bedroom plan with bathroom on each side.  Two Large master suite type bedrooms with new toilets and facets .  Kitchen has been upgraded with granite counters, soft close draws and doors and Stainless steel appliances ('22&'23).  Kitchen features a breakfast nook with more large windows (2 sets) and a set of large sliding glass doors separating this space from your enclosed Florida Room. Spacious hall pantry.  Master shower has been beautifully upgraded with new piping and tile stretching floor to ceiling. The whole home was re-piped in Sept '23. New Water heater ' July '23.   Updated paint throughout, new 2" faux wood blinds and new carpet in the bedrooms ('22) Upgraded electrical includes LED lighting and energy efficient fans, smoke detectors, new outlets throughout the Lanai, Pool area and around the outside and solar landscape lighting.  Updated irrigation lines, heads, new filter on separate well for irrigation system along with new timer.  New window screens and Hurricane Shutters for piece of mind.  Side entry garage.  Take a look and stop shopping :)
